Package: GLMsim
Type: Package
Title: A GLM-based single cell RNA-seq simulator incorporating batch and biological effects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Jianan", "Wang", email = "wang.j@wehi.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jianan Wang <wang.j@wehi.edu.au>
Description: This package aims to capture library size, biological variation, unwanted variation, and their associations via a generalized linear model, and simulate data resembling the original experimental data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
